me":"2020-07-31T11:40:12.000Z","msg":"點睇到佢叫雞？<br />\n<br />\n利申絲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb309e976748a2e0d1209302bc4a575a54581c8e","tid":2133903,"uid":123774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"11667e570596a862856ae9cdc2746463a749f592","tid":2133903,"uid":148817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T11:40:12.000Z","msg":"點睇到佢叫雞？<br />\n<br />\n利申絲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T11:41:44.000Z","msg":"兆豐樓"},{"pid":"1d60e23e3e0b111045ebc87e6029728b7cf43fa9","tid":2133903,"uid":40470,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"11667e570596a862856ae9cdc2746463a749f592","tid":2133903,"uid":148817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T11:40:12.000Z","msg":"點睇到佢叫雞？<br />\n<br />\n利申絲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T11:42:08.000Z","msg":"兆豐樓出名<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5d37b3c46e6120416cc80ef64b0713b9944d170","tid":2133903,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T11:44:22.000Z","msg":"😂😂😂😂😂😂"},{"pid":"e860b0414a3ce2d90f22c838998783ad94bdaeee","tid":2133903,"uid":224561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T11:44:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c601e8f4fc3e22757813b555450a6d5e6c9e112","tid":2133903,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T09:48:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7fd3d11ccaed565d61f42f2937d160c39a3b2d4c","tid":2133903,"uid":360603,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T11:25:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />傳銷臭雞 專呃身邊d朋友上去 為既只係令到自己可以上41 入面d人比人洗曬腦 日日搞埋d心理堂 紅酒班 依家有人確診真係傳銷死全家<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"991f014fd663e142fb8370ea505a29cadff19b77","tid":2133903,"uid":94151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-02T10:37:35.000Z","msg":"近期有追開/讀呢間 石天（中學）既人都會好清楚 <br />\n我地出左幾個高收入人士 又買樓 又渣波子 又買錶<br />\n整個頭都4000蚊 家陣疫情 4000蚊已經做到好多野<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tcrh10S.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ftcrh10S.png&h=381683ef&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1nNAOHH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1nNAOHH.png&h=d4f84941&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jx8TBff.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fjx8TBff.jpg&h=92532650&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PLwaDtA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPLwaDtA.jpg&h=4b2381e6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2FYXitB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2FYXitB.jpg&h=8ac45eb8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8QX1K8B.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8QX1K8B.jpg&h=52b5e38d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n然後莉姐(許巧莉 41 準備升42) 係石天中學搵到兩位下線<br />\n<br />\n分別係第2位老千:湛灝霖同第3位老千:佢女朋友關嘉儀<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NCWRnbm.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNCWRnbm.png&h=3c221c3f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/O1VrbdJ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FO1VrbdJ.png&h=fc290575&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WMh5rNo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWMh5rNo.jpg&h=779de6df&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ixjb6Np.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fixjb6Np.jpg&h=82f27bb2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UTv6VFM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUTv6VFM.png&h=e20aba24&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RLeO80N.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRLeO80N.jpg&h=28afb748&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n兩位做到風山水起 又買樓又買錶<br />\n成日話SELL到貨比人係自己本事 一買一賣<br />\n但會唔會有sales 會sell到個客成身債 破哂產?<br />\n湛灝霖仲係中學個GROUP入面搵食 比人拆穿左就同人嘈交<br />\n<br />\n莉莉BB 亦都同樣係中學GROUP搵食 仲話有好野益大家<br />\n大家快D做佢既38<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rKkOszG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrKkOszG.jpg&h=43207433&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Z7O8szJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZ7O8szJ.jpg&h=ca786584&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/auOz7zK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FauOz7zK.jpg&h=26983957&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kKUrYGr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkKUrYGr.jpg&h=df0ebd9b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n佢D朋友叫解釋下間公司背景 產品<br />\n就話人唔了解佢 有人作野打擊佢間公司<br />\n大佬呀 我地做客戶都想了解下公司既產品啦<br />\n<br />\n第4位老千 : 感恩姐(黃錦恩)<br />\n<br />\nE位黃錦欣睇黎真係不嬲都大仆街黎，識著佢既朋友真係慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/t5x1DAD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ft5x1DAD.jpg&h=84e6c9e5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n佢中學嗰陣時已經識得成日搵着數 之前仲有幫元氣壽司賣廣告 <br />\n可能佢覺得自己讀ece懷才不遇所以轉行做老千<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5BwmDCn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5BwmDCn.png&h=a43a2b2a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n究竟真係uber eat搵佢定係佢自己叫外賣然後扮KOL呢？十分好奇<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wX0fcEo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwX0fcEo.jpg&h=82c36812&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SwFiUSK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSwFiUSK.jpg&h=5d8174eb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dtyTJL5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdtyTJL5.jpg&h=b7158d58&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kUOz7CM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkUOz7CM.png&h=7eb1df29&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n講到幾咁想幫人 要幫人發達<br />\n實際係要人借錢借到盡 升做41 咁佢就可以湊夠6個41 升做42<br />\n睇黎佢幫人負債係有一手<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ODv6Ymi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FODv6Ymi.jpg&h=1386d948&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n伯母洗緊既1萬蚊 洗完會折福<br />\n污糟錢黎 成手血呀伯母<br />\n<br />\n第5位老千: 鵬燕玲<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GONMYmJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGONMYmJ.jpg&h=7fc98825&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AS5bp1K.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAS5bp1K.jpg&h=028e18bf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RjgaHU9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRjgaHU9.png&h=3850c8ca&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n身為幼稚園老師 呃左人40萬 幾時還返D錢比人呀?<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pfhUrsH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpfhUrsH.png&h=8a07127d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hrBh8F3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhrBh8F3.png&h=a6ae56db&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n呢堆老千為左錢不擇手段 連有精神病患既人都搞<br />\n為左錢 令到人冇左份工 再借左財仔40萬 人地點哂你名呀<br />\n許巧莉 湛灝霖 關嘉儀 黃錦恩<br />\n你地點樣補償返呢位苦主? 人地就黎要跳樓"},{"pid":"00ec987c51be05e5e8c036927400c4d0be4ea2bc","tid":2133903,"uid":340278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-02T11:03:31.000Z","msg":"推"}]}